name: Sultans of the Osmerian Relic
description: Hailing from the searing apex of Mt. Kalfus, the Sultans of the Osmerian Relic are known to frequent Cinderkeep and consort with the mad wizard Zephyrial. One of the few who witnessed the Osmerian Anomaly, and equipped with the knowledge of what may have actually happened, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
